Li = eval(input())
Imax = int(max(Li))
Imin = int(min(Li))
Nmax = Li.count(Imax)
Nmin = Li.count(Imin)
a = 0
b = 0
if Imax != Imin:
    while a < Nmax:
        Li.remove(Imax)
        a += 1
    while b < Nmin:
        Li.remove(Imin)
        b += 1
    print(Li)
elif Imax == Imin:
    Li.clear()
    print(Li)
